This paper deals with the experimental characterization and mitigation of errors in NAND flash memory, which is a topic that falls under the scope of computer architecture (cs.AR), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), systems and control (cs.SY), embedded systems (cs.ET), and software engineering (cs.SE).
